    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>《EXODUS™》是一款科幻动作冒险角色扮演游戏。你会在其中扮演一名巡星使，带领人类对抗辰族，为生存而战。你需要面对早进化40000年的人类后裔，探索各种神奇美丽的星球，并挑战时间那能够影响数代人的力量。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/9e9c0798228cc716c4808d47e0a5f985.poster.avif?t=1767810085\" width=720 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/9e9c0798228cc716c4808d47e0a5f985.webm?t=1767810085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/9e9c0798228cc716c4808d47e0a5f985.mp4?t=1767810085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>留下一份塑造未来命运的遗产</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演俊·阿斯兰，从一名拾荒匠成长为传奇巡星使——一名穿梭于星际之间的反抗者和搜寻古代秘密的猎人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成星际任务，回收可能掌握着人类生存关键的辰族遗物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你回到你的世界时，会发现一切已经沧海桑田——时间膨胀效应会放大你的选择，改变人类的未来。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/8b30f98b06506ab72ab292598995676c.poster.avif?t=1767810085\" width=720 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/8b30f98b06506ab72ab292598995676c.webm?t=1767810085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/8b30f98b06506ab72ab292598995676c.mp4?t=1767810085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>带领人类为救赎而战</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与敌人展开激烈的战斗，包括怪物般的外星生物和构造体，敌对的人类王朝，以及最大的威胁——辰族。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合遗物与人类科技，壮大你的军火库，并使用只有你能够操纵的护手释放威力强大的技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与实力不俗、性格各异的伙伴并肩作战，凭借他们的力量、技能和默契配合来扭转不利的战局。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/3600fef4245af798dea9c7547bba57f1.poster.avif?t=1767810085\" width=720 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/3600fef4245af798dea9c7547bba57f1.webm?t=1767810085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230960/extras/3600fef4245af798dea9c7547bba57f1.mp4?t=1767810085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索神奇的世界，结识杰出的伙伴</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个充满惊奇和奥秘的星系，领略诡谲壮观的星球，遭遇各种独特的生物，并一路建立（或打破）各种羁绊。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗那早已进化的人类后裔——Celestial，包括由基因工程打造的异变种，以及高度智能的觉醒种动物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领一支所向披靡的小队穿越群星。你的队员包括人类和觉醒种，他们都有自己的动力和信念，能够在未来的战斗中为你提供巨大的助力。</p></li></ul>",
